EntityQueryParsingException
public abstract static class EntityQueryParsingException.ExpressionUnbalanced extends EntityQueryParsingException
Base class for unbalanced exception, meaning a token or keyword was expected but not found. The EntityQueryParsingException.getErrorExpressionPosition() will contain the position of where the token was expected.
